reviews: Great hoodie for the cold spring and autumn days. Nice and warm and soft to the touch. No complaints. Ordered 2xl for myself. I'm 6ft, 250.

Bought the 2xl for myself. I'm 6 foot, 250lbs. It fit great. Not too big and definitely not baggy. Fits well around the arms and chest and is the average length. You can lift your arms straight up and the shirt will not show any skin. It's a nice quality, a little big soft to the touch. The red and white print on the black shirt looks awesome.

I'm ordering the other color sets.

reviews: Bought this as a gift for my daughter, but the little guy seems to have disappeared. Thank god.

All photos in the calendar from the reputation tour. Great swag.
Love it
Fit the person I bought it for perfectly. High quality hoodie at a reasonable price.

review_title: Fits big and long. Recommend 1 size down.
reviews: Great quality and well made hoodie, but fits a size up. Usually fit a true 2xl, but this fits like a 3xl.
Works great, fits well. Keeps my head warm.

Bought these thinking that since they're golf gloves they'd be great. Shovelled twice and the leather cracked and stretched out on the pointer and middle finger. You can feel the cold right through where it cracked. They sit on the dresser and bound for the garbage.

review_title: No repeat colors, not too thin. Cheap.
reviews: Lots of different colors all the same style, a 22 Ã— 22 square thin cloth. Washed them with a little salt and vinegar to set the colors. Dried them on the delicate cycle and they're ready to go. Nothing to complain about. I'd buy them again if I somehow lost all my favorite colors.

review_title: Untested, unwashed, but they look good.
reviews: Haven't had a chance to do anything more than try them on, but they look as good as the Propper brand pants which I wore for years at a previous job. Hope they stand up well. Arrived a business day early which is always nice. Size 40 waist, 32 inseam. Yes they have a button fly. Throwback....

reviews: As the title says...

review_title: Comes with an OK screen protector.
reviews: Straight up 4 stars. I like it for the price. Somewhat easy to install and included glass or plastic screen protector is nice. (I cant tell which it is). Only complaint is that the SP is a tad too small for my Samsung a20.
The product you info is spot on. The main reason I bought it was for the battery backup. Holds your time when it's unplugged and alarm works when unplugged.
I like this shirt. Soft, well made fabric. Fits a little loose for a standard 2x. Very soft nice feeling fabric. Almost a hip hop style of shirt. 5 outta 5.
Love this mount. Easy to install. Came with lots of screws, washers and fasteners. Recommend. 5 outta 5.
Good fit for a size 38 waist. Fabric doesn't have much give and gets tight in the bottom of the crotch. They're good but not great. Just OK. 3 outta 5.

This is a good quality shirt. Front design looks good. It's a strong medium/heavy material. Didn't shrink much and most importantly a true 2xl. I ordered another LRG shirt and it fit 2 sizes too small but this one fits perfect.

review_title: Does its job but rusts quick.
reviews: Luke the title says. Spend the extra money to buy stainless steel. The nickel plating helps but not around the edges. Rusted immediately.
